TITLE: Migration Generation Script with Atlas
DESCRIPTION: Main script for generating database migrations using Atlas format, setting up the migration directory and configuration options.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ent/ent/blob/master/doc/md/versioned-migrations.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_8

