TITLE: Defining Custom Field Type for PostgreSQL Domain in Go
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to create a custom field type for a PostgreSQL domain in Go. It defines a 'DomainString' type that wraps a string and implements the 'driver.Valuer' and 'sql.Scanner' interfaces for database operations.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ent/ent/blob/master/examples/compositetypes/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: Go
CODE:
