TITLE: Defining Domain Type in SQL
DESCRIPTION: SQL code to create a domain type for US postal codes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ent/ent/blob/master/doc/md/migration/domain.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
CREATE DOMAIN us_postal_code AS TEXT
CHECK(
   VALUE ~ '^\d{5}$'
   OR VALUE ~ '^\d{5}-\d{4}$'
);
```

