TITLE: Adding Comments to Ent Edges in Go
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to add documentation comments to edges that will appear in the generated entity code. Shows support for multiline comments using escape sequences.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ent/ent/blob/master/doc/md/schema-edges.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_32

LANGUAGE: go
CODE:
```
// Edges of the User.
func (User) Edges() []ent.Edge {
	return []ent.Edge{
		edge.To("pets", Pet.Type).
			Comment("Pets that this user is responsible for taking care of.\n" + 
				"May be zero to many, depending on the user.")
	}
}
```

