TITLE: Creating Test Database Schema
DESCRIPTION: SQL commands to create test tables for users and cars with a foreign key relationship
SOURCE: https://github.com/ent/ent/blob/master/doc/website/blog/2021-10-11-generating-ent-schemas-from-existing-sql-databases.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
create table users
(
    id        bigint auto_increment primary key,
    age       bigint       not null,
    name      varchar(255) not null,
    last_name varchar(255) null comment 'surname'
);

create table cars
(
    id          bigint auto_increment primary key,
    model       varchar(255) not null,
    color       varchar(255) not null,
    engine_size mediumint    not null,
    user_id     bigint       null,
    constraint cars_owners foreign key (user_id) references users (id) on delete set null
);
```

